rules.sql: encounterId is not null AND encounterId != ''
rules.name: EncounterIDmustbepresent

rules.sql: patientMrn is not null AND patientMrn != ''
rules.name: PatientMRNmustbepresent

rules.sql: encounterCode is not null AND encounterCode != ''
rules.name: Encountercodemustbepresent

rules.sql: encounterCodeSystem is not null AND encounterCodeSystem != ''
rules.name: Encountercodesystemmustbepresent

rules.sql: admitDate is not null AND admitDate != ''
rules.name: Admitdatemustbepresent

rules.sql: dischargeDate is not null AND dischargeDate != ''
rules.name: Dischargedatemustbepresent

rules.sql:
TRY_CAST(admitDate AS DATE) < '1900-01-01' 
OR TRY_CAST(admitDate AS DATE) > CURRENT_DATE
rules.name: Encounterdatesmustberealistic
EncounterdatesdischargeDatemustberealistic
rules.description: Encounter dates dischargeDate  must be realistic

rules.sql: DATEDIFF('day', TRY_CAST(admitDate AS DATE), TRY_CAST(dischargeDate AS DATE)) > 365
rules.name: Lengthofstay>365days

rules.sql:
providerNpi IS NOT NULL 
AND providerNpi != '' 
AND providerNpi NOT RLIKE '^[0-9]{10}$'
rules.name: NPIshouldbe10digits

rules.sql: dischargeDisposition IS NOT NULL AND dischargeDisposition != ''
rules.name: Dischargedispositionvalueanalysis
